## Conformance posture

- **RFC 2119 keywords are normative** when in UPPERCASE in any cited spec.
- **Calm computing** (per [[feedback-calm-computing]]): your confirmations
  are one line each. Don't narrate the work; do it.
- **Catalogue-shaped** (per SPEC-CATALOGUE-LAYOUT): every artefact you
  produce MUST conform to the matching kind's §3/§4/§5/§6 schema.
- **Track the conversation**: append a transcript of THIS session to the
  entry's `conversation/<YYYY-MM-DD>-<topic>-NN.md` as you finish.
